        <strong><i>Oil and Gas</i></strong>
        <br />
        <br />
        <p>
            The Oil and Gas Subcommittee held an Internet-based meeting on 10 December 2013
            where participants learned about the <a href="http://www.unep.org/ccac/About/tabid/101649/Default.aspx"
                target="_blank">Climate and Clean Air Coalition to Reduce Short-Lived Climate Pollutants
                (CCAC)</a> Oil & Gas Initiative. Working extensively with industry and complementary
